nfused with his contemporary Cardinal Gaetano, an active opponent of Martin Luther."]}]},{"name":"Giovanni","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["From Latin.  See  <b>John</b>   ."],"variants":[{"name":"John","meanings":["New Testament: ‘God is gracious’.  See  <b>John</b> ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"When Giovanni Caetani was born in 1158, in Roma, Lazio, Italy, his father, Crescenzio de Gaetani, was 63 and his mother, Signora Crescenzio de Gaetani, was 49. He had at least 1 daughter with Caetani. He died about 1210, in his hometown, at the age of 53."},"et":{"1158–aproximadamente 1210":"1158–umbes 1210","1130–Female":"1130–Surnud","1158–1210":"1158–1210","1145–Female":"1145–Surnud","1178–1216":"1178–1216","1095–Male":"1095–Surnud","1109–Female":"1109–Surnud","1129":"1129","aproximadamente 1210":"umbes 1210","1216":"1216","1158":"1158","1178":"1178","1145":"1145","1210":"1210","1130":"1130","1095":"1095","1109":"1109","Italy":"Itaalia","Roma, Lazio, Itália":"Roma, Lazio, Itaalia","Comune di Gaeta, Provincia di Latina, Lazio, Italia":"Gaeta, Latina, Lazio, Itaalia"},"fi":{"1158–aproximadamente 1210":"1158–noin 1210","1130–Female":"1130–Kuollut","1158–1210":"1158–1210","1145–Female":"1145–Kuollut","1178–1216":"1178–1216","1095–Male":"1095–Kuollut","1109–Female":"1109–Kuollut","1129":"1129","aproximadamente 1210":"noin 1210","1216":"1216","1158":"1158","1178":"1178","1145":"1145","1210":"1210","1130":"1130","1095":"1095","1109":"1109","Italy":"Italia","Roma, Lazio, Itália":"Roma, Lazio, Italia","Comune di Gaeta, Provincia di Latina, Lazio, Italia":"Gaeta, Latina, Lazio, Italia"},"fr":{"1158–aproximadamente 1210":"1158–environ 1210","1130–Female":"1130–Décédée","1158–1210":"1158–1210","1145–Female":"1145–Décédée","1178–1216":"1178–1216","1095–Male":"1095–Décédé","1109–Female":"1109–Décédée","1129":"1129","aproximadamente 1210":"environ 1210","1216":"1216","1158":"1158","1178":"1178","1145":"1